episodes.title: Disturbing Internet Cults
episodes.description:
Online, every connection feels harmless, until you realize who’s really on the other end. In today’s video, we’re getting into the disturbing world of internet cults. From the horrifying group known as 764, to the twisted ideology of the Order of Nine Angles, these aren't just fringe communities. They are sadistic nightmares.

These cults use forums, encrypted apps, and even mainstream platforms to spread influence, manipulate minds, and push people toward unthinkable actions. 

WARNING: This video includes references to extremely disturbing content, including violence, radical ideology, and psychological manipulation. Viewer discretion is advised.

If you’re drawn to internet mysteries, true crime, or the dark psychology behind people, this video and channel is for you. Please like and subscribe, it helps more than you know, thank you. 

Edited by - @editedby_le on X

Stay curious. Stay cautious. And stay safe.
